# PocketForge WiFi credentials for the boot-resource FAT partition.
# Copy this file to wifi.txt and fill in your network details.
# wifi.txt is gitignored — it contains your WiFi password.
#
# Format: key=value, one per line. Comments (#) and blank lines are ok.
# Required: SSID, PSK
# Optional: KEY_MGMT  (default: WPA-PSK)
# Optional: POWER_SAVE (default: off) — WiFi radio power-save policy.
#   off : stability-first (recommended). Best for game streaming; avoids the
#         xradio deauth/reassociate flap. Battery is managed by screen-off/suspend.
#   on  : let the radio doze when idle (small battery gain, may flap on xradio).
SSID=YourNetworkName
PSK=YourPassword
